{%- comment -%} Product FAQ Section {%- endcomment -%}
<div class="product-faq">
  <h2 class="product-faq__title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  <div class="product-faq__item">
    <h3>Why a display and not a mobile app-only solution?</h3>
    <p>Apps are amazing but an app alone can be easy to ignore, forget about, and doesn't foster independence in little ones who don't have a phone. The Hearth Display is physically in your home and acts as a hub for your family to be organized every day.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="product-faq__item">
    <h3>When will my Hearth Display Ship?</h3>
    <p>Your order will process within <strong>2 business days</strong>. Once shipped, you'll receive a confirmation email with tracking details.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="product-faq__item">
    <h3>Do I need a family membership subscription to use the display?</h3>
    <p>The family membership is optional. Your first month is free! Membership unlocks all features for $9/month or $86.40/year (save 20%).</p>
  </div>
  <div class="product-faq__item">
    <h3>What if I change my mind about my Hearth Display?</h3>
    <p>There is a 30-day return period. If you change your mind, just send it back for a refund.</p>
  </div>
</div>

